#: code:addons/snailmail_account_followup/wizard/snailmail_letter_format_error.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Payment reminders / follow-ups can not be updated and resent this way. They "
"have to be sent again in the same way as they were originally sent."
msgstr ""
"No es posible actualizar y reenviar los recordatorios de pago o de "
"seguimiento de esta manera, debes volver a enviarlos de la misma forma en "
"que los enviaste originalmente."

